      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOL THE JETS (1) returns. Worth noting he filled a minor placing when returning from a spell last time in work over a similar trip at Penola. Rates highly on best form and can return with a bang. YOURAWAY (4) turned in a strong run two starts ago at this track then struggled to back it up at Terang last time. Goes well at this shorter journey so looks a leading contender. JUST WAI (7) has a moderate winning strike-rate but was a big improver here third-up when finishing third. Strips fitter and has enough dash to offset the tricky draw and give another bold sight. THE STREAKER (5) returns from a spell and did win first-up last time in work over this trip at Port Augusta. Fitter for a recent trial win at Murray Bridge. Genuine hope. CROWN MOSHE (8) also returns and looks best of the rest.",
